metadata.description: Reftest run in Stylo vs. Gecko mode ([Treeherder push](https://treeherder.mozilla.org/#/jobs?repo=mozilla-central&revision=b2a9a4bb5c94de179ae7a3f52fde58c0e2897498))
metadata.name: test-linux64/debug-reftest-stylo-e10s-8

command:
:: sccache currently uses the full compiler commandline as input to the
:: cache hash key, so create a symlink to the task dir and build from
:: the symlink dir to get consistent paths.
if exist z:\build rmdir z:\build

"c:\Program Files\Mercurial\hg.exe" robustcheckout --sharebase y:\hg-shared --purge --upstream https://hg.mozilla.org/mozilla-unified --revision b2a9a4bb5c94de179ae7a3f52fde58c0e2897498 https://hg.mozilla.org/mozilla-central .\build\src
